stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: agent calls skill_manage
    Created --> Active: written to ~/.hermes/skills/
    Active --> Pinned: agent or user marks pinned
    Active --> Stale: 30 days unused
    Stale --> Active: agent uses it again
    Stale --> Archived: 90 days unused
    Pinned --> Pinned: immune to auto-transitions
    Archived --> Active: user restores
